Steps to Customize and Deploy:

1. Replace Placeholder Content: Update the movie images and titles, and add valid YouTube trailer links for each movie in the "Top 5 Movies" section.


2. Deploy: You can easily deploy this website on platforms like Netlify or Vercel:

Create a GitHub repository for the project.

Link the repository with Netlify or Vercel.

The site will be live once the deployment is completed.




